    • Constructor Detail

      • TransformerDistribution

        public TransformerDistribution​(X distribution,
                               Function<Double,Double> transform,
                               Function<Double,Double> inverseTransform,
                               Function<Double,Double> inverseTransformDifferential,
                               double meanPrecision,
                               double sdPrecision)
        Parameters:
        distribution - - the pre transformation distribution X. when we want the distribution of Y
        transform - - Y = g(X) what is the transformation of X that gives us Y? e.g. Y=e^X
        inverseTransform - - Y = g^{-1}(Y) what is the inverse? X=log(Y)
        inverseTransformDifferential - - dg^{-1}/dy the differential of the inverse with respect to Y? e.g. DY = 1/Y
        meanPrecision - - the quantile limit of the integration to estimate the mean
        sdPrecision - - the quantile limit of the integration to estimate the sd
